    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "@minrk, @ellisonbg: do you guys think we could make mathjax loading optional? There are a number of scenarios where we've seen it can cause problems, so it might be worth making it optional (if nothing else, if a user has forgotten to install it locally and they don't have internet, they're hosed and can't even open their files).  I'm making this a blocker so that at least we make a decision for 0.12, even if the decision is to for now leave it as-is... Just so it's high on our radar of things not to forget.\n\nI'd vote for making it optional, on by default but easy to disable...\n"
  },
