    "body": "Since mathjax is so huge, it makes sense for it to be optional.  Should this be a server-level config?  Ideally, it would be per-browser (stored in a cookie), since you can connect to a single server from both fast and slow connections, making it server-level is probably a good idea.\n\nI think our need to have a little control panel (must be on the front page, because it has to be prior to loading a notebook) and mechanism for storing some config browser-side is getting severe.\n"
  },
